Dear Santa...

Dear Santa,

This year I've been busy!

Last month I turned in for eating carbs (3 points). In January I bought porn for (10 points). Last Monday I signed my organ donor card (28 points). In March I set 's puppy on fire (-66 points). Last Saturday I pushed in the mud (-17 points).

Overall, I've been naughty (-42 points). For Christmas I deserve a moldy sandwich!

Sincerely,
quarters69
